</RadzenText>

<RadzenText TextStyle="TextStyle.Body1" class="rz-my-6">
    The <code>RadzenSkeleton</code> component is used to display loading placeholders while content is being loaded. 
    It supports different shape types (Text, Circular, Rectangular, Rounded) and animation types (Wave, Pulse) that can be combined independently.
</RadzenText>

